---
title: Cheesy Beef & Veggie Baked Gnocchi with Sugo Sauce
description: Knock knock. Who's there? Gnocchi! It's been roasted, then baked with a veggie-loaded tomato and beef sauce and cheesy topping, so we're pretty sure you'll want to invite it in for dinner!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5dba2bf26742ca2a4b65ca4c-7d8376d2.jpg
